===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# [[impulsive|Impulsive]] and [[unpredictable]]; [[determine]]d by [[chance#Noun|chance]], [[impulse]], or [[whim]].
#: {{synonyms|en|arbitrary|whimsical|fickle}}
#: {{antonyms|en|conscientious|rigorous}}
#: {{ux|en|I almost died in a '''capricious''' winter storm.}}
#: {{ux|en|Stringent rulers are unlikely to act '''capriciously'''.}}
